	Research Interests&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;My research lies at the meeting ground of algebra, number theory and algebraic geometry. More precisely, I am primarily interested in various properties of algebraic groups over non-algebraically closed fields, with special focus on local and global fields. I also study linear representations of finitely generated groups using the technique of representation varieties and try to understand the phenomenon of representation rigidity.&lt;/p&gt;
